```plantuml
@startuml UoA-eResearch_hub-stack

actor User

participant "ResearchHub Website (Frontend)" as Frontend
participant "GraphQL API (cer-graphql)" as GraphQLAPI
participant "Search Proxy (hub-search-proxy)" as SearchProxy
participant "Contentful"
participant "Elasticsearch"
participant "AWS S3"
participant "CloudFront"
participant "AWS Lambda"
participant "Jenkins"
participant "Terraform"
participant "AWS"

== User Access Flow ==
User -> Frontend: Access ResearchHub Website
Frontend -> CloudFront: Request static assets
CloudFront -> AWS S3: Fetch static assets
AWS S3 -> CloudFront: Deliver assets
CloudFront -> User: Rendered assets

== Data Fetching ==
User -> Frontend: Request content
Frontend -> GraphQLAPI: Fetch content via GraphQL
GraphQLAPI -> Contentful: Proxy request for content
Contentful -> GraphQLAPI: Return content data
GraphQLAPI -> Frontend: Deliver content data

== Search Functionality ==
User -> Frontend: Initiate search query
Frontend -> SearchProxy: Send search request
SearchProxy -> Elasticsearch: Query Elasticsearch
Elasticsearch -> SearchProxy: Return search results
SearchProxy -> Frontend: Deliver search results

== Content Update ==
Contentful -> SearchProxy: Notify content update
SearchProxy -> Elasticsearch: Update index with new content

== CI/CD Deployment ==
Jenkins -> Terraform: Trigger infrastructure updates
Terraform -> AWS: Deploy infrastructure changes

@enduml
```